Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.85,0:01:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！从森林那边来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是四魂碎片啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.46,0:02:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让蜈蚣突然变得凶暴的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是有什么事情尽管叫我就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师大人 谢礼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.05,0:02:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我收下这个就好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.59,0:02:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是从我们村里出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.22,0:02:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 珊瑚登场！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天上有好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些星星的数量和四魂碎片的数量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个比较多呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来前面还有很长一段路要走啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.14,0:02:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.01,0:02:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落那混蛋也跟我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在收集着四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样还可以省下不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让那家伙去收集 然后我们一拼抢过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个计划不错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到的四魂碎片越多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落就会变得更强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到那时候就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们得抢先收集更多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像我这种小孩子都懂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么就不懂呢？真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脑子到底有多蠢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.25,0:03:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收集到所有碎片以后有什么打算？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用问嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要变成真正的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不够强就什么都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算遇到看不顺眼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不够人家强的话就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.34,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你藉助四魂之玉的力量变成完全的妖怪以后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还能保持自我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过有谁用四魂碎片的力量做好事的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到四魂之玉之力的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时 也会失去心智
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得自己说过要变成好妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 你想要保护戈薇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你需要力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你利用四魂之玉变成妖怪之后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可能就会把戈薇小姐和七宝吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都要吃？就不吃弥勒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一早逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说八道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在为止跟四魂之玉扯上关系的妖怪们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.24,0:05:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本就都不是好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.67,0:05:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为那样罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我…不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人把四魂碎片拿走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候拿走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！快说！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有妖怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去找除妖师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.83,0:05:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大蜈蚣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:27.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪里像了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说除妖师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来还有人以除妖为职业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个除妖师在收集四魂之玉的碎片吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:43.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 她还说那个叫什么的玉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从她的村子流落出去的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你知道这件事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道有四魂之玉的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已经由桔梗在守护着了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉是怎么来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 你回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猎物是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.48,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蜈蚣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带回来一些脚和皮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用来制作盔甲吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖哦 乖哦 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.43,0:06:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有做好孩子啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首领叫你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 你得到四魂碎片了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.95,0:06:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样能镇住碎片的邪气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:06:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概50年前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把玉交给一位灵力高强的巫女保管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并由她净化着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到那位大人最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是在争抢玉的战斗中去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是在找到能够净化玉的灵力高强的人之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把碎片收集到村里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并小心守护了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,净化玉的灵力…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.69,0:07:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就又有工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 你也要做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经11岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多该参加实战了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪真的会喷火喷毒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 你害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.22,0:08:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才没害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要收拾的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是一些大蛇和大蜘蛛罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最可怕的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.36,0:08:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伪装成人类的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.96,0:08:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种妖怪要是得到四魂之玉就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.74,0:08:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 你们来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只大蜘蛛每晚都会来袭击城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城中已经有数人被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有办法收拾它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 请交给我们处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从村里挑选了几个高手来除妖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你说的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是像女人一样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连小孩子都有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在下的女儿和儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们村是数一数二的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.17,0:08:59.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就请您见识他们的身手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到没？要加油哦 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父…父亲这个大骗子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公 它来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有妖怪出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主的病之所以久治不愈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.69,0:09:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因为妖怪的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.59,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公已经找来了除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场喧闹也只到今夜为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.96,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后只需期待少主您早日康复了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除妖师？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它围起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 琥珀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 压制住它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:41.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为珊瑚是村里最好的高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子就把那个大蜘蛛给…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.65,0:10:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它脑袋打烂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.52,0:10:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是块头大了点 没什么了不起嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.17,0:11:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在太简单了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只蜘蛛的妖气也很弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 为什么要把父亲他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀 住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…连我都不认识了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 除妖师！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随他们去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.85,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是有趣的余兴节目
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了？琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.14,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丝…是蜘蛛丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你干的好事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对姐弟都发疯了 杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐…姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.39,0:13:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.19,0:13:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥珀！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.36,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射下一箭 对准发疯的两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琥…琥珀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐…我好怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别怕…有我在…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两姐弟和好了啊 可喜可贺可喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主…主公…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.69,0:13:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主 主公他到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是我父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.17,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就觉得父亲不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是被妖怪附身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:05.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜了那些除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们埋到庭院一角去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然没一个人知道除妖师的村落在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只知道在山里面啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 总之去找就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 你要去除妖师的村子抢四魂碎片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别反而被除掉了就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 人家似乎是专业高手诶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我也很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉为何会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.39,0:14:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还说四魂之玉本来就出自他们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.62,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也一定很想知道原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事…真是让人讨厌的风
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么正在接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且数量很多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一大群妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的妖气…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是一般的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 诡异得让人恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们想去攻击什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.90,0:15:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那对除妖师姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看看还很小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可怜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.18,0:15:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.55,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么…能死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女除妖师？你还活着啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们多年来对除妖师的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎都发泄完了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.24,0:16:48.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好心告诉你们这个山寨的除妖师都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们居然连我都想攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知好歹的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.18,0:17:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那些妖怪的目标…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.89,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟妖怪战斗过了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.81,0:17:54.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我们一直在找的除妖师的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没有四魂碎片的气息呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全被抢走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.29,0:18:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去追的话说不定能追上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把这些村民埋葬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有妖怪活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个声音是犬夜叉少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会说话？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静下来 云母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.66,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人不是你的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想念您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.14,0:18:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认识啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是犬夜叉的家臣 算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.81,0:19:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 这里是除妖师隐居的村落
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个村子里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.69,0:19:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎世世代代都是除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪那些妖怪会这么怨恨他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是偏偏趁这个时候来袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的高手都被召入城中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚好是村子的防御最薄弱的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心里面一直觉得很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被召入城中的人们没事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.68,0:19:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少还有你一个人活了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 除妖师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.75,0:19:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不回答少主
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做珊瑚对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的父亲 还有弟弟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和同伴都…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:56.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？为什么会发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听从您的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快马加鞭 赶到了除妖师的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到村子里的人都被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是遗憾啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.66,0:20:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本来还想向村里人打听许多事情的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.96,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指四魂之玉的事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冥加爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:37.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是在这里调查玉的事情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很早以前就十分在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉到底是什么东西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为跟玉扯上关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后都会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追踪着四魂之玉的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就来到了这个村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过有一件事我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:21:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中一直都能看到一个白狒狒的身影出没
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白狒狒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.95,0:21:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落…他就在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把详细情况告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在除妖师的村落看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.74,0:21:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了横尸遍野的村民
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和袭击村子的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉企图利用四魂之玉的妖力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成完全的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能他认为能在除妖师的村落得到四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才会袭击那个村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞来骨还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.21,0:21:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个袭击村子的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去杀了那个叫犬夜叉的半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}我们在生命的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.80,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&H77D68D&\3c&H244D2C&\4a&H00&\c&HC1D4C8&}逐渐失去一切
